e=1> No, the problem is that based on the Verant vision of the wizard class, warriors are NOT supposed to be primary damage dealers, they take damage, but wizards are SUPPOSED to be the primary damage dealing class in the game.<br>
<br>
Now, the problem is that with the Velious and Kunark weapons, haste, strength, dex, and agility buffs, warriors do a LOT more than just take damage.  They become a primary damage dealing class.  Wizards, who are supposed to be primary damage dealers, well, we arn't over an extended period of time.  I have said this directly to Absor in a chat I had with him on the EQ chat server, but it doesn't seem to have done any good.  Melees still get all their buffs, and casters(and wizards in particular), get treated like garbage.<br>
<br>
 <p>Targonis Manastorm<br>
